statements: SELECT id, dataset_name, query_description, result_visualization FROM visualizations_data;
SELECT result_visualization, query_description, dataset_name, id FROM visualizations_data;
SELECT dataset_name, result_visualization, query_description, id FROM visualizations_data;

SELECT * FROM visualizations_data WHERE id=1;
SELECT * FROM visualizations_data WHERE id = 1;
SELECT dataset_name, query_description FROM visualizations_data WHERE id > 3 ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT dataset_name FROM visualizations_data WHERE id IN (2, 4);
SELECT * FROM visualizations_data WHERE id <= 3 OR dataset_name LIKE '%sample%' ORDER BY id, dataset_name DESC;
SELECT id, result_visualization FROM visualizations_data WHERE dataset_name IS NOT NULL AND id BETWEEN 2 AND 4 ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT * FROM Table1;
SELECT column1, column2 FROM Table1 WHERE column2 > 100;
SELECT column2, column3 FROM Table1 WHERE column1 = 'value';
SELECT column1, column3 FROM Table1 ORDER BY column3 DESC;
SELECT * FROM Table2 WHERE column2 LIKE '%value%';
SELECT column1, column2, column3 FROM Table1 WHERE column2 > 100 ORDER BY column2 DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT DISTINCT column1 FROM Table2 WHERE column3 = '2022-01-01' ORDER BY column1 ASC;
SELECT column2, column1, AVG(column3) AS average_value FROM Table1 GROUP BY column2, column1 HAVING AVG(column3) > 50;
SELECT column1 AS label, CONCAT(column2, '-', column3) AS concat_values FROM Table2 WHERE column2 LIKE '%example%' ORDER BY column1;
SELECT * FROM Table1 t1 INNER JOIN Table2 t2 ON t1.column2 = t2.column1 WHERE t1.column3 > 100 AND t2.column3 > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM visualization_metadata;
SELECT visualization_name, visualization_type FROM visualization_metadata ORDER BY visualization_name DESC;

SELECT query_text, created_date FROM visualization_queries ORDER BY created_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT query_id, query_type, created_date FROM visualization_queries WHERE query_category IN ('report', 'dashboard') ORDER BY created_date DESC;

SELECT visualization_type, COUNT(*) FROM visualization_data GROUP BY visualization_type;
SELECT query_result->>'start_date' AS start_date, query_result->>'end_date' AS end_date FROM visualization_data WHERE visualization_type = 'Line Chart';
SELECT q.id, q.query, a.analysis_result, v.type_name FROM query_results q JOIN statistical_analysis a ON q.id = a.analysis_id JOIN visualization_types v ON a.visualization_id = v.id;
SELECT v.type_name, a.analysis_result->>'mean' AS mean_value FROM statistical_analysis a JOIN visualization_types v ON a.visualization_id = v.id WHERE a.analysis_id = 12345;
